filters

Class DanceFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • filters.AdvancedFilters
      • filters.DanceFilters

  • public class DanceFilters
extends AdvancedFilters
    DanceFilters is a VBox which is placed on the Search page. It contains various filter options for conducting a dance search, such as specifying type, number of bars, couples, set shapes, author, formations, and steps
    Author:
    Jack
